# PR Review / Merge Strategy

> **Always-on merged rule:** `.cursor/rules/maintainer-delivery-loop.mdc` — use that for enforcement in chat; this file remains a focused reference.

PRs should:

- explain why and risk, not only what changed
- include validation/evidence appropriate to impact
- note migration or compatibility implications

Avoid merging changes that skip known release or safety gates.

